body: Test to solve jitpack compile problem.

NOTICE: We've cleaned our dependency repository, older Foundation versions than this will not compile. If you want to download Foundation, download its latest version, or simply update dependencies in pom.xml yourself copying over from this version's pom.xml

- Update plugin dependencies to their latest versions.

- Fix Remain#json for MC 1.18+
- Added two new item sliders by @CoobMC

- Updated NBT library for Minecraft 1.18.2

## DO NOT USE YET

Foundation 6 is work in progress. We are recording our new trainings and will gradually release test builds which are non-production ready.

Please wait patiently until this notice is removed. If you are a student of MineAcademy, you will get an update about this. If you are not, we also plan to release free YouTube videos in Q2 this year so no worries :)

Save comments for YamlStaticConfig classes by default. Removes the need to override saveComments() > true method.

* We now register settings.yml and localization/ files automatically. Thus removed the need to use getSettings in your main plugin class and the call to Lang.init(). Existing plugins will not break.
* No longer initializing classes when using ReflectionUtil#getClasses. 
* You can now run async blocks of code in commands using "runLater" and "runAsync" methods in the SimpleCommand class directly. If you used Common#runLater before you know that tell() would not work, it will work if you call runX methods from SimpleCommand since we handle that.

- Improved and safer nickname support in HookManager
- More customizable YamlConfig, Menu and SimpleCommand classes
- New methods to FileUtil
- Automatically migrate Bungee_Server_Name to server.properties file
- Few typos corrected

- Added broadcast... methods to Messenger
- More Minecraft 1.7.10, 1.6.4, 1.4.7 and even 1.2.5 compatibility layers, although things outside of what we use in our premium plugins will necessarily break due to lack of APIs.. if you need specific thing working, open a pull request
- Added ASCIIUtil
- Tab completions are now sorted A-Z
